As an intern at a language learning, gamified application start-up, I've utilised a range of design skills.

Some of my responsibilities during my internship at Taplingua include:

-Work on the Android and iOS user interface using Material design.

-Optimised user flow for onboarding, lessons, leaderboards, etc.

-Work on gamification, monetisation, and user retention.

